_sText:
It is a small map
based off a construction site in gta 4
only took about 2 days
i used Z's compiler program which has recently been updated
24 spawn points

and there will be a custom nav file soon made by Chizbone (for final version only)

i used a skybox made by karatekafer

changes/additions
took out the annoying engine sound
added some nature sounds 
deleted most of the explosive barrels and other annoying props
added a small trailer (new t spawn)
made it a little brighter 
its a little bigger than last time with a little more space to move around
added some overlays
made it a little bit brighter (doubt it will be noticeable) 
fixed the invalid spawn points


ideas for final version:
trees 
city environment skybox
more sounds

any other suggestions anyone has for this map would be greatly appreciated 

I'm not going to get a good nav file done until the final version is done 
unfortunetly chizbone made a nav file last night for the first beta and it never got used and now beta 2 is out but thanks chiz your great :)



EDIT :
the crane is climbable all the way to the top  only where there is a ladder though
